Name: Kitty Hawk
About the game: Fly through a neon, virtual reality paradise as Kitty Hawk, the inter-dimensional voyager. Navigate through strange structures, avoid fireball-hurling monkeys, dodge ravenous space bats, and most importantly--never give up. The controls are simple. Flap your arms to soar. Hit the trigger for a boost. The objective is clear. Survive as long as you can. Grab precious gems for points.
